cs.RO, cs.SD, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing a multimodal pouring network for service robots. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper uses audio data to improve the accuracy of the pouring task. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a neural network-based approach for pouring task estimation. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely as the paper does not rely solely on vision-based methods for pouring task estimation. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also less likely as the paper does not focus on control theory or system design.
